                  </hi>. I am clerk to Mr. Prestor—I saw the defendant on the subject of this affidavit—I read it over to him, and went with him to be sworn and saw him sworn.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18760808-name-288" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18760808-name-288" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
