                  </hi>. I am a barge builder, of 14, Rotherhithe Walk—I was a witness on the trial of Jones <hi rend="italic">v.</hi> Coombe—until yesterday I did not receive any money for that; I then received five guineas.</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="187608080097"></xptr>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined.</hi> I know the defendant quite well—I should have had no objection to take his word for the money—I did not look to him, I looked to Mr. Preston.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18760808-name-290" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18760808-name-290" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
